flowchart TD
  A[Trigger: Monthly warranty cost data update from SAP S/4HANA]
  A --> N1[Stream: DDM/Crawlers - Ingest monthly warranty cost data]
  N1 --> N2[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Analyze monthly warranty cost trends]
  N2 --> N3[Cortex: RCA Service - Identify top warranty concerns by component/system]
  N3 --> N4[Cortex: AutoML - Benchmark dealer performance]
  N4 --> N5[Stream: STREAMS - Link field quality reports to warranty claims]
  N5 --> N6[Cortex: Cortex Auto Forecast - Forecast future warranty costs]
  N6 --> N7{Decision: Select and schedule monthly warranty cost analysis actions and determine key drivers to report for COGS impact and potential cost reductions}
  N6 --> Z1[Outcome: Reduced COGS and improved profitability through cost containment and supplier/part-level risk mitigation]
  N7 -->|High variance in warranty costs| B1[Initiate detailed RCA analysis]
  B1 --> O1[Outcome: Identify underlying issues]
  O1 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Underperforming dealer identified| B2[Schedule intervention meeting]
  B2 --> O2[Outcome: Improve dealer performance]
  O2 --> End[End]
  N7 -->|Significant increase in predicted war...| B3[Trigger cost containment measures]
  B3 --> O3[Outcome: Reduce COGS]
  O3 --> End[End]
  Z1 --> End[End]